OL,3,CAttempted murder charge after stolen
OL,4,CMercedes hits man in Westcliff
OL,6,FA man has been charged with attempted
OL,7,Fmurder after a pedestrian was struck
OL,8,Fby a stolen car in Westcliff.
OL,10,FEssex Police were called at around
OL,11,F7.30am on Thursday 16 April to
OL,12,FCrowstone Road, following reports a
OL,13,Fwhite Mercedes C Class car,
OL,14,Fregistration YD14 OHT, had struck a
OL,15,Fman before the vehicle left the area.
OL,17,FThe 50-year-old man received treatment
OL,18,Ffrom members of the public, officers
OL,19,Fand ambulance service colleagues. He
OL,20,Fwas taken to hospital, where he
OL,21,Fremains in a critical condition.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/2
