OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776625869
OL,3,CAttempted murder charge after stolen
OL,4,CMercedes hits man in Westcliff
OL,6,FOn Sunday, 26-year-old James Wallace,
OL,7,Fof no fixed abode, was charged with
OL,8,Fattempted murder and handling stolen
OL,9,Fgoods, and remanded in custody to
OL,10,Fappear at Basildon Magistrates' Court
OL,11,Fon Monday 20 April.
OL,13,FPolice are still appealing for any
OL,14,Finformation about the movement of the
OL,15,FMercedes, in particular in the areas
OL,16,Fof Sutton Road, Crowstone Road and
OL,17,FBritannia Road on Thursday 16 April.
